Emotion:

Paranoia.

Players watch everyone.

Every negotiation matters.

Every investment matters.

Every purchase matters.

Players begin asking:

"If I do this...

...what will everyone else do?"

This is the emotional peak of Ledger.

Final Two Players

Emotion:

Respect.

